suvvipada
rAga AnandaBairavi AditALa
suvvi SrIdEviramaNa suvvi sarvarAjaSayana
suvvi daityanikaraharaNa suvvi nArayNa |
Bavyacarita duritavipinahavyavahana BavEMdrAdisEvyamAna suprasiddha sulaBamUrutE
avyayAtmanE suKAtma ninna divya mahime tutipa

suvvivEkigaLige koDuvudamitamOdava || 388 ||
vAsavAdyamaravAtASiSAradeMdumadhva- dESikAryacitta
siMhapIThamadhyaga dESakAlavyApta
sarvESa sArvaBauma SrImahIsamEtakRuShNa koDali namage mOdava || 389 ||
kamalasaMbavana vEda tamanu oyyutiralu lakShmiramaNa matsyanAgi tanda Saradhi mathanadi
kamaTharUpadinda surarigamRutavittu kAyda aKiLasumanasEMdrasvAmi koDali emage maMgaLa || 390 ||
kanakalOcananna sadadu manujasingavEShanAda
dyunadipaDeda janani kaDidu vanava carisida
janapakaMsanodadu tripuravanitesuvratavanaLida
vinuta kalki dEvarAja emma salahali || 391 ||
pAhi pAvannacarita pAhi pAhi padmanEtra
pAhi nigamanikarastrOtra lalitagAtra mAM
pAhi sujanastOmamitra dOShadUra suguNa sandOha jagannAtha viThThala jaya tridhAmaga || 392 ||